[16/05/2017 14:22:56] <font color="#ffffff">-MACV, Military</font>
[16/05/2017 14:22:56] <font color="#ffffff">Assistance Command Vietnam...</font>
[16/05/2017 14:22:57] <font color="#ffffff">...y Spanish Medical Mission.</font>
